Another record breaking @socceraid for @unicef_uk. Thanks for your support and helping us raise an incredible £13,014,769.
 
There’s still time to donate and help even more children > socceraid.org.uk/donate

node.text:
Looking forward to linking back up with a few former @manchesterunited and @england teammates at @socceraid for @unicef_uk this Saturday. 🙌

We take on the #SoccerAid World XI at The Etihad Stadium this Saturday, 7:30pm kick-off. It’s all for a great cause. Limited tickets still available. See link in bio! 💙🌎⚽️
